{"tid":522693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利迷無資格笑我地阿仙奴","createTime":"2018-01-07T18:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T04:14:37.000Z","uid":5655,"like":114,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f29866f5924976f4a68099bfed0bd2979141bd87","tid":522693,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:37:23.000Z","msg":"你話獌狗 車狗笑尻我地<br />\n我地認我地柒<br />\n係今年打得差<br />\n抵比人笑<br />\n<br />\n但講到柒<br />\n利物浦遠遠超過阿仙奴<br />\n季賽又屌鳩古天奴 25 又話佢懶<br />\n都人哋俾心機幫你踢 你又當佢神咁拜<br />\n到而家轉會又話人哋狗<br />\n咩古天奴死老母<br />\n斷腳空難死<br />\n咁撚柒嘅球迷都係第一次見"},{"pid":"d0dfcd2406115b9fdb972f088e2e041c32aa1e85","tid":522693,"uid":133100,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:38:13.000Z","msg":"死毒撚車迷又想扮阿狗牙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edab79aa2581f54bf8edc4541d8f461ce9ed6975","tid":522693,"uid":581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0dfcd2406115b9fdb972f088e2e041c32aa1e85","tid":522693,"uid":133100,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:38:13.000Z","msg":"死毒撚車迷又想扮阿狗牙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:39:07.000Z","msg":"唔好屈"},{"pid":"1690c20cf00d141d78bdcc998a75d97f5899da95","tid":522693,"uid":43666,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"講到當年批阿狗無屌過法比咁 <br />\n而家我利屌隻25古關唔關你事啊"},{"pid":"56915b732545c247af76b6c2519bd06580625fdf","tid":522693,"uid":1139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:39:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16e383783768061d016a952a806803031a72b9ba","tid":522693,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"笑4"},{"pid":"edacd44f1405b9b3989744329e697c34b0500cd8","tid":522693,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1690c20cf00d141d78bdcc998a75d97f5899da95","tid":522693,"uid":43666,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score